This location seemed to have gone through many different drinking spots, and I've gotta say this current spot has the best food and drinks by far. It's a cute place with outdoor seating, bright indoor area with tables, and a darker indoor booth seating area. Tried a few different things to eat and everything's been pretty consistent and good. It's good vibes. Pretty decent for a casual night out with friends
